-- Manchester United, GM’s Chevrolet Agree on Jersey Sponsor Deal
-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 2012-07-30T14:51:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-30/manchester-united-gm-s-chevrolet-agree-on-jersey-sponsor-deal.html
Manchester United, the record 19-
time English soccer champion, said General Motors Co.’s
 Chevrolet  unit will be the team’s jersey sponsor for seven years
from the 2014-15 season.  No financial details were revealed in a United release.
Chevrolet is currently the club’s official car partner.  The car company will replace Aon, whose partnership with
United began in the 2010-11 season, United said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  